requirements.text:
Add the Google Ads tracking tag (gtag.js) to the website's HTML <head> section in frontend/index.html by inserting the following script block before the closing </head> tag:

```html
<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=AW-17968689708"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'AW-17968689708');
</script>
```

Ensure the script loads asynchronously and initializes the Google Ads conversion tracking with ID AW-17968689708.
